"Classification of abode" means one of the following types of abode licensed or certified by a State agency:
Related institutions under § 19-114 of the Health - General Article;
Private or public group homes under § 7-601 of the Health - General Article;
CARE homes under Title 6, Subtitle 5, Part II of the Human Services Article;
Adult foster care homes regulated by the Department of Human Resources; or
Senior assisted housing facilities under Title 10 of the Human Services Article.
